'''iproute2''' is [[Article description::a tool developed to unify network interface configuration, routing, and tunneling.]]

iproute2 provides the {{c|ip}} command for this purpose.

== Ethernet interface configuration ==

=== List available interfaces ===

{{Cmd|ip link|output=<pre>
